{"tid":1831282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國反對排除華為在德國5G網絡建設，否則德國的5G恐怕會滯後幾年","createTime":"2020-01-20T09:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T12:54:35.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aeca7f9d3dbbedae5b61fb63435af3ebe697c06e","tid":1831282,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503580-20200119.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503580-20200119.htm&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV98TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=e059582a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503580-20200119.htm&h=7d49ac9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503580-20200119.htm</a><br />\n德國內政部長澤霍費爾表示，反對將中國電訊設備商華為，排除在德國5G網絡建設之外，否則德國的5G建設，恐怕會滯後幾年。<br />\n<br />\n澤霍費爾說，反對因為可能有事發生，而將某一種產品逐出市場，亦反對貿易壁壘，又說如果無華為的參與，看不到德國可以在短期內建成5G網絡。至於涉及的安全考慮，澤霍費爾認為在必要情況下，可以增加額外的安全保障。"},{"pid":"1a97d1345b13e397cab643a2ea50b1cb3b3d8afc","tid":1831282,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddce0f3a061c1cb861c4bd1f98935157fe018ff8","tid":1831282,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:41:32.000Z","msg":"作為前輩，對後輩好係應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5701f555adaa4c6c7b12ba48dcc8144331a313c8","tid":1831282,"uid":254183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"台灣不靠支為<br />\n今年七月5G就正式商轉<br />\n德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188caa61a4c98075f13641dffe7ad7e9962dfe9d","tid":1831282,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5701f555adaa4c6c7b12ba48dcc8144331a313c8","tid":1831282,"uid":2541